description: Got a sweet-tooth craving? Not Just Icing is roaming the streets of Durham, looking to serve up some sugary sweet treats. At Not Just Icing, they believe that cupcakes are so much more than just a great tasting icing - they've got the whole cupcake package! From the icing to the soft velvety cake, your taste-buds are sure to be in heaven. Choose from a variety of delectable flavors. Vegan and gluten-free options are also available for purchase.
name: Not Just Icing
